### Version
2.6.10

### Reproduction link
[https://output.jsbin.com/daroyiz](https://output.jsbin.com/daroyiz)







### Steps to reproduce
测试代码如下：
```
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>Vue 测试实例 - 菜鸟教程(runoob.com)</title>
<script src="https://cdn.bootcss.com/vue/2.6.10/vue.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
<div id="app">
	<div v-for="item in list">
		{{item.name}}
		<child @done="display(item, $event)"></child>
	</div>
	<button @click="add">添加</button>
</div>
<script>
var Child = {
	template: "<span>子组件</span>",
	mounted: function (){
		this.$emit('done');
	}
};
new Vue({
  el: '#app',
	components: {
		child: Child
	},
  data: {
	  list: [{name:"张三"},{name:"李四"}]
  },
	methods: {
		display: function (item){
			console.dir(item.name)
		},
		add: function (){
			this.list.unshift({name:"王五"})
		}
	}
})
</script>
</body>
</html>
```
点击添加按钮控制台打印的总是李四，而不是王五。

### What is expected?
display方法得到的item总是最新添加的元素

### What is actually happening?
display方法得到的是list的最后一个元素

